# UI icons and copy

- Do not use emoji characters in user-visible UI (screens, buttons, toasts, empty states).
- Use **lucide-react** icons only for glyphs and affordances. Store habit icons in the database as Lucide component names (e.g. `Flame`, `BookOpen`) and map them to components with a single dynamic resolver (see `components/HabitIcon.tsx`).
- Prefer the app accent **#ec5b13** (`text-primary` / `bg-primary`) on light **neutral** surfaces; keep layouts readable and consistent with existing `(app)` shell patterns.
